channel.title: {Getting Server Online}(HELP)
channel.description:
Okay, i need help to get my server so people can actually join using a no-ip,
_______________________________________________________________________
Downloaded no-ip. (www.no-ip.com) Downloaded All Stuff For Server. I got a brain I got a computer.. i got source i got my server so that i can play, and edit on it. I NEED MY SERVER ONLINE
Can anyone help ________________{Summary}_____________________________ I downloaded no-ip and i created a host, (Leaderscape.no-ip.biz) I need help port forwarding.. so i went to portfoward website.. then i typed in default ip address for forwarding i typing in default username and password.. i went to applications & Gaming. i went to port range forwarding and i dotn know what to put into the Start ~ End Port boxes, and i Ip address ~ To Ip Address.. i also have no clue what with application names..
So if you could just post exactly what i put into each box to make my server online, and have a default port (43594)
Thanks, Josh
